data.text:
The PFF U19 Boys National Championship National Group Stage is set to kickoff this Saturday 14 May 2022 in both the PFF National Training Center in Carmona, Cavite and Tionko Football Field in Davao City, Davao del Sur.

The first set of fixtures sees Laguna-Cavite RFA battle Cordillera RFA in the first game and South East Luzon Masbate RFA taking on U15 champions National Capital Region FA in the second Group A to be played in Carmona.

Group B fixtures in Davao sees Mount Apo RFA take on SOCSARGEN RFA in the opening match followed by Zamboanga Del Norte-Dipolog FA against Davao South RFA.

The National Group Stage will be held from 14-22 May 2022 with the top two teams advancing to the Final Round which will be played on June 2022.
